result.name: Victory Asian Limited T/A The Lifestyle Kitchen

reviews.text: Good services and good quality food

講人情味的地方. A place where they treat you like old friends. Food is generally always good. Except the sashimi. Well which is not bad but how good their sashimi can get after all this is a place for hotpot. Ironically, the ladies always try their best to sell you those sashimi with all kinds of discount, in a friendly way. Which is the reason this place worth one star less. You'll have a good night IF you start by going with their flow. Just chill and let the hotpot food (and the amazing broth) speaks for itself.
Worthy hotpot and the sashimi is very fresh
Very local and good quality of food, with unbelievably cheap price!

result.name: 金筷子火鍋小廚

reviews.text: Best hotpot spot in san po kong!
我覺得佢地嘅地方都算可以，d姐姐都好好人好友善，不過我通常都10點後先去，因為有75折，真係抵食好多，但係好似只係星期一至四先有75折。
被坤，明明介紹$288海鮮拼盤，黎到重諗住有兩碟咁抵，又介紹蝦魚menu冇，又話老闆自己做好彈牙，點知柴嘅，問佢幾錢話幾十，咁埋叫埋！點知單到，海鮮$238+188，蝦丸$98！嘩，同佢理論又話咩咩咩，邊會有咁平巴巴巴...總之唔會再去！重有，識食牛一食佢啲牛揾野𢲡過...𢲡到林哂冇哂牛味，黑店一間！
地方狹窄，晚上可擺枱門外食，除食物新鮮，無乜特別，總括價錢都算貴，可以一試。
